to get inside their robots heads.

00:03:53.849 --> 00:04:05.090
Using ceiling mounted projectors, animation
software, and motion capture technology these

00:04:05.090 --> 00:04:27.850
holo-testing grounds can visualize a robot’s
intentions in real time.

